{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-post-template-tsx","path":"/posts/abcs-grep-r","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"33a878e8-3894-5f4c-be7b-240e1779d820","html":"<h2 id=\"r\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#r\" aria-label=\"r permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>R</h2>\n<p>Use the <code class=\"language-text\">-r</code> and <code class=\"language-text\">-R</code> flag to <strong>recursively</strong>​ search through directories.\nThe only difference between the two is <code class=\"language-text\">-R</code> will follow symlinks in subdirectories.</p>\n<p>Let’s suppose we have a subdirectory called <code class=\"language-text\">alpha</code> with a file\nnamed <code class=\"language-text\">alpha.txt</code> that contained the following:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">// Located in ./alpha/alpha.txt\nHello alpha!</code></pre></div>\n<p>Use an <strong>asterisk</strong> to search through all files in the current directory.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ grep \"Hello\" *\ngrep: alpha: Is a directory</code></pre></div>\n<p>Since <code class=\"language-text\">alpha</code> is a directory, use the <code class=\"language-text\">-R</code> flag to recursively search through it.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ grep -R \"Hello\" *\nalpha/alpha.txt:Hello alpha!</code></pre></div>","fields":{"slug":"/posts//posts/abcs-grep-r","tagSlugs":null},"frontmatter":{"date":"2023-11-18","description":"What does grep -[rR] do?","tags":null,"title":"The ABC's of grep - R","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts//posts/abcs-grep-r"}},"staticQueryHashes":["251939775","2764776372","401334301"]}